=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以前師傅就話，如果冇乜車要讓，可以入定1波+左腳磨擦點+右腳腳掣，一鬆腳掣就去得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"上斜好驚溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前上斜紅綠燈2波一停就轉燈(我係第一架)，結果心急無拉手掣直接1波，唔知係咪踏唔實brake成架車溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後斜路話知後面係咁響你，拉完手掣空波再入1波算，始終呢個方法平時做開<br />\n<br />\nbtw 永考街有咩需要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"2波都可以開車既，吊既位再要高啲，個時比師父屌話2波開車唔係唔得，考試就唔好喇，容易死火，其實你緊張啫，1波吊返磨擦點都唔會溜後"},{"pid":"5a852280e8cdf12b170f9b9af27126bc472fafdb","tid":1124681,"uid":47972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71c46386f5c2434532e2c3723c7fff7240165167","tid":1124681,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">第一次考，有咩要注意？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"叫你師父幫你避開死亡考官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />渣得自信啲比考官覺得比你pass唔係馬路炸彈"},{"pid":"cb9da2f90006e9b3cc097b0ce6d470e6c84727f4","tid":1124681,"uid":154487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5689ee9972ee01c39e7f60c8317c6d3ad5a41a2","tid":1124681,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb0d21c17df8eccd4d284bc5a5963c40c07d3f1f","tid":1124681,"uid":34553,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"忠孝街轉入迦密村街時<br />\n盞右綠燈出咗先好轉<br />\n唔係就一個大剔話你唔讓對面行車線"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:54:41.000Z","msg":"即係袋口位等一陣先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"我琴日岩岩考完忠義Pass<br />\n都係又係入迦密 入面好多死車 記得做足望鏡盲點"},{"pid":"83214962d71126fb8b60caab8eb27bfa0bef9817","tid":1124681,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"迦密村街真係睇時段， 我當年考嗰陣順到仆街乜車都冇"},{"pid":"bed5013a1d3d00fb22f2569900c1eeaf5af8c9c0","tid":1124681,"uid":60131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89c38eb0ded5d0d3eb4a5cbc2260ee901dd1914a","tid":1124681,"uid":58223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86ecd27e69ef7502f855df20cac9e9d4bd8da677","tid":1124681,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c10ae1bcca64924ca2ca8b533cd83f4b04ba63b0","tid":1124681,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:02:12.000Z","msg":"讓線係唔係點都停定拉手制隱陣d?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"考牌讓線都一定要停低望架喇<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你停定 見到冇車先慢慢入波 磨擦點 鬆手掣 可能後面已經有車黎到<br />\n<br />\n唔知你師傅有冇教你可以唔拉手掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以前師傅就話，如果冇乜車要讓，可以入定1波+左腳磨擦點+右腳腳掣，一鬆腳掣就去得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"上斜好驚溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前上斜紅綠燈2波一停就轉燈(我係第一架)，結果心急無拉手掣直接1波，唔知係咪踏唔實brake成架車溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後斜路話知後面係咁響你，拉完手掣空波再入1波算，始終呢個方法平時做開<br />\n<br />\nbtw 永考街有咩需要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"認真，考試用最熟悉嘅方法就好，唔好搞咁多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考試凡斜路開車老虎蟹都拉緊手掣、吊好極力子先再起步，最穩陣就和多少少油先再放手掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0148d2598337c4951ce1bdffe1b5c9eef3694a2d","tid":1124681,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:29:12.000Z","msg":"巴打搵師父？<br />\n有好野可推介？"},{"pid":"1ecf1dbc37b574a2fa6305ffedf12a4ab78e7d03","tid":1124681,"uid":31405,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"臨行車時，考牌官會叫你可以開始<br />\n到時大聲講，I have control !!<br />\n再同考牌官講，依家我地人車合一<br />\n車在人在<br />\n車亡人亡<br />\n<br />\n車牌xxxxxx ， 出發"},{"pid":"22d55548f28f86d27c79e23e2cc157de148b9941","tid":1124681,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83214962d71126fb8b60caab8eb27bfa0bef9817","tid":1124681,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"迦密村街真係睇時段， 我當年考嗰陣順到仆街乜車都冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"幾點咁順？"},{"pid":"c44e423f405b9b1c50bd7108bc59bc1dc76fc4f0","tid":1124681,"uid":9617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"Ching,我都係下個禮拜考忠義街自動van,我都好驚路面狀況惡劣肥，大家一齊加油啦"},{"pid":"6f8b0b2296b6242e9158de3f4dffa5b1b84da50d","tid":1124681,"uid":66172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T01:42:11.000Z","msg":"迦密村街入面會有好多死車, 需要踩埋對面線過死車, 但因為啲死車會阻住你前方視線, 有機會你一爬頭對面其實會有車黎緊, 到時就玩撚完, 所以小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋小路出大路一定要望清楚, 唔駛心急, 確定冇車衝緊過黎先好出<br />\n祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cff309b3160135edeea60e99e6113c25bd18cf","tid":1124681,"uid":213214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"肥硬架啦～唔使諗<br />\n唔肥又點pass？"},{"pid":"22061b8bdd0e5507da098974ac95c69cae2f83b3","tid":1124681,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:22:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只係一個運氣遊戲</span>"},{"pid":"c2216e5aab491e2fb3a071b9083d6f28752c235e","tid":1124681,"uid":90884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:50:53.0